  "내용": "<p>대표님, 2026년 소상공인 정책자금이 <strong>총 3조 3,620억 원</strong> 규모로 공급됩니다. 시중은행보다 훨씬 낮은 금리와 유리한 상환 조건으로 영세 사업자를 지원하는 정부 융자 제도의 핵심을 정리해드립니다.</p>\n\n<h3>2026년 소상공인 정책자금 핵심 수치</h3>\n\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:24px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:140px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0066CC 0%,#0052A3 100%);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:4px;\">3.36조원</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">총 공급 규모</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:140px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10B981 0%,#059669 100%);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:4px;\">연 2.96%</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">기준 금리</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:140px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#F59E0B 0%,#D97706 100%);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:4px;\">최대 5억</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\">융자 한도</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h3>자금 유형별 금리 비교</h3>\n\n<div style=\"margin:24px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#F8FAFC;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">일반경영안정자금</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#0066CC;\">2.96%</span></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#E5E7EB;border-radius:4px;height:12px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg,#0066CC,#3B82F6);height:100%;width:60%;border-radius:4px;\"></div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">성장기반자금</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#10B981;\">2.76%</span></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#E5E7EB;border-radius:4px;height:12px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg,#10B981,#34D399);height:100%;width:55%;border-radius:4px;\"></div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">청년고용연계자금</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#F59E0B;\">3.56%</span></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#E5E7EB;border-radius:4px;height:12px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg,#F59E0B,#FBBF24);height:100%;width:72%;border-radius:4px;\"></div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:6px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">시중은행 대출 (참고)</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#EF4444;\">5~8%</span></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#E5E7EB;border-radius:4px;height:12px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg,#EF4444,#F87171);height:100%;width:100%;border-radius:4px;\"></div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#F0F9FF;border-left:4px solid #3B82F6;padding:16px 20px;margin:24px 0;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n  <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:15px;color:#1E40AF;\">💡 비수도권 우대</h4>\n  <div style=\"color:#1E3A8A;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">비수도권 소재 사업자는 <strong>0.2%p 금리 우대</strong> 혜택을 받습니다. 지역 격차 해소를 위한 정책입니다.</div>\n</div>\n\n<h3>2026년 1월 신청 일정</h3>\n\n<div style=\"margin:24px 0;overflow-x:auto;\">\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:white;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;\">\n    <thead><tr>\n      <th style=\"background:#F3F4F6;padding:12px;text-align:left;border-bottom:2px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">자금 유형</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#F3F4F6;padding:12px;text-align:center;border-bottom:2px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">1차 접수</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#F3F4F6;padding:12px;text-align:center;border-bottom:2px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">2차 접수</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#F3F4F6;padding:12px;text-align:center;border-bottom:2px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:600;color:#374151;\">3차 접수</th>\n    </tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:600;color:#111827;\">직접대출</td><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;color:#0066CC;text-align:center;font-weight:600;\">1/12(월)</td><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;color:#4B5563;text-align:center;\">2/2(월)</td><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;color:#4B5563;text-align:center;\">3/3(화)</td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;font-weight:600;color:#111827;\">신용취약자금</td><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;color:#0066CC;text-align:center;font-weight:600;\">1/19(월)</td><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;color:#4B5563;text-align:center;\">2/9(월)</td><td style=\"padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E7EB;color:#4B5563;text-align:center;\">3/9(월)</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#FFFBEB;border:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:24px 0;\">\n  <h4 style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#92400E;\">⚠️ 조기 마감 주의</h4>\n  <div style=\"color:#78350F;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;\">예산 소진 시 조기 마감될 수 있습니다. <strong>1월 접수 시작 즉시 신청</strong>하시는 것이 유리합니다.</div>\n</div>\n\n<h3>가점 대상자</h3>\n\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:12px;margin:24px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#F0FDF4;border:1px solid #BBF7D0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"font-size:24px;margin-bottom:8px;\">👨‍💼</div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#166534;\">재창업 소상공인</div></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#FEF3C7;border:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"font-size:24px;margin-bottom:8px;\">👩‍🦱</div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#92400E;\">청년 (만 39세 이하)</div></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#F0F9FF;border:1px solid #BAE6FD;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"font-size:24px;margin-bottom:8px;\">♿</div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#0369A1;\">장애인 기업</div></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#FCE7F3;border:1px solid #FBCFE8;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"font-size:24px;margin-bottom:8px;\">👩‍💼</div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#9D174D;\">여성 기업</div></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>※ 출처: 중소벤처기업부, 소상공인시장진흥공단 (2026년 공고 기준)</p>\n<p>※ 문의: 중소기업통합콜센터 1357 / 정책자금 전담 1811-3655</p>",
